</exercise>
<exercise>
    <introduction>
        <p>
         Determine the actual change in population each year and the relative change in population each year.
        </p>
        <p> 
            note:The actual change is <m>y_2-y_1</m> and the relative change is <m>(y_2-y_1)/y_1</m>
        </p> 
    </introduction>


